QuestData.Title: Surprise the Sashj'tar
QuestData.Description: The naga are preoccupied with recruiting the sea giants for Queen Azshara's battles in other lands.$B$BNow is the time to strike!
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 12 Sashj'tar Champions or Sashj'tar Deep Witches in Azuregale Bay.

Objectives.Objective: Sashj'tar Champions or Sashj'tar Deep Witches slain
